{"tid":952326,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"提出BNO平權 HK Watch五位patrons之一 英國前上議員、自由民主黨領䄂Paddy Ashdown離世","createTime":"2018-12-23T04:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T06:51:03.000Z","uid":48083,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d818bbf1eae41624d60b434cadd8509d218dc7c4","tid":952326,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯Paddy Ashdown 嘅貢獻<br />\n<br />\nPaddy Ashdown 好多香港人未必認識佢太多，但如果話佢係Hong Kong Watch五位Patrons之一，提出BNO應該平權果位上議院議員，咁大家知佢係邊個，所以Liberal Democrat係特別喺黨嘅悼念聲明中，提到佢promoting the right&rsquo;s of the citizens of Hong Kong，亦都係咁解。佢同早好多離開人世，令BN(HK)A 1997同埋BNA 1981 Section 4B BNO 修訂部分成為現實嘅Lord Avebury，都係為香港人打到底嘅英國政界人士，我個人經驗，喺品格上， Liberal Democrat 好多資深政客，係比保守黨唔少人值得尊敬，我作為一名保守黨黨員都要咁講。<br />\n<br />\nPaddy Ashdown嘅離世，對香港人係重大損失，無錯，彭定康想幫香港人做好多嘢，但礙於佢係最後一任總督嘅身份，同埋佢同保守黨千絲萬縷嘅關係，好多人未必方便由佢老人家出手，好多時佢老人家已經做咗好多喺英國朝野慣例上破格嘅事，Paddy Ashdown 可以 take unpopular causes，例如 BNO 平權，喺之前大家都無信心英國政界會接受，但依家已經去到Rees-Mogg相關人物喺House of Commons接手(當然同SNP爭緊)，香港人某程度上，係欠咗 Paddy Ashdown 。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得如果香港人係有心，寫封信去Liberal Democrat 或 Hong Kong Watch 表達對Lord Ashdown嘅敬意，或者用以下電子悼念冊，紀念呢位曾經為香港出唔少力嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.libdems.org.uk/book-of-condolence-paddy-ashdown\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.libdems.org.uk%2Fbook-of-condolence-paddy-ashdown&d=wNStLeKlJHZ9UhUikNHI4ZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=d8fba359\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.libdems.org.uk/book-of-condolence-paddy-ashdown</a><br />\n<br />\n對香港有恩嘅人，都值得我們去紀念，不論國籍、種族同身份。<br />\n<br />\n黃世澤<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/23527/paddy-ashdown-離開人世\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F23527%2Fpaddy-ashdown-%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%96&d=wNStLeKlJHZ9UhUikNHI4ZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=5023ca76\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/23527/paddy-ashdown-離開人世</a>"},{"pid":"72ea95642cf972d1f916eaab0f11f54861c69d04","tid":952326,"ui